 of a company.</li><li>Conducted psychological test scoring and interpretation and then wrote psychological assessment reports under the psychologist\'s supervision.&nbsp;</li><li>Conducted training need analysis with the client for developing the training modules. Planned training activities with the trainer and team. Supervised team\'s work performances and responsible to facilitate client\'s needs while doing the training program.</li><li>I support the psychologist in counseling by interviewed the client to find out the problem they are faced.&nbsp;</li></ul><h6><b>Program Associate at Kita Berkisah&nbsp;</b></h6><h6>2021<b> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</b></h6><h6><ul><li>Kita Berkisah is enganged in mental health to make it easier for everyone to access mental health services, with our tagline \"A safe space for expression, empowerment, and growth\".</li><li>I managed several responsibilities such as: developing and planning projects that related with mental health issues.</li><li>Researching and conceptualizing event\'s guide with evidence-based articles.&nbsp;</li></ul></h6><p><o:p></o:p></p><p><o:p></o:p></p><h6><b style=\"font-size: 0.9rem;\">Peer Counselor at Female in Action</b></h6><h6><span style=\"font-size: 0.9rem;\">2021</span></h6><h6><ul><li>Receive a case report from women who had mental health problems.&nbsp;</li><li>Through FIA Care, an application that connect females with counselors, I provide support for females in working with their challenges or issues affecting their well-being.&nbsp;</li><li>Trained to be a professional peer counselor.&nbsp;</li></ul></h6><p><o:p></o:p></p><p></p>', NULL, 'https://calendly.com/virendaruttp/consulting', NULL, NULL, '2021-11-24 07:12:22', '2022-02-13 21:15:43'),
